{"tid":521374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國人惡行】赴日狂掃福袋轉售 日人嬲爆：唔好再嚟啦","createTime":"2018-01-06T13:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T14:10:09.000Z","uid":51904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9cbe9fc641de5f2396d3ae3930d93058ffb50c7","tid":521374,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"中國人不時都會上日本新聞及節目，日本人對他們的好感度不斷下降。最近，中國人轉賣福袋的事情更上了新聞，令其他排隊買福袋的日本人相當不悅，朝日電視台的晨間節目《モーニングショー》，早前派節目製作團隊去拍攝大型電器店的福袋隊列，雖然只是晚上10時，但已有大批人到場排隊，當中有不少人來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n當福袋開賣後，部份買到福袋的人跟隨門外的中國人指示，走到停車場進行交易。他們在停車場大概有四輛車，全部都裝滿大型電器店鋪的福袋，節目嘗試向他們進行採訪，但有些人說「這是替朋友買的，他們現在走開了，很快會回來。」有些人甚至大吼：「很吵啊！這些都是買給自己的！」<br />\n<br />\n隨後，節目工作人員在網上發現，中國網站有招聘告示「1月1日在新宿排隊的工作」，報酬有5,000元日圓（約345.51港元）以上，並會採用50人以上。而且，他們在中國購物網站上，找到店家以6.8萬元日圓（約4,700港元）賣出價值6萬元日圓（約4,100港元）的福袋，更誇張的是，他們聲稱庫存達約1,300個，許多日本民眾暴怒：「如果是以轉售為目的而來，希望他們不要再來。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180106/57672196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57672196&d=6I%2BpkoK27cGef97SsFlBogHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1d413c62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57672196&h=ac738ea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180106/57672196</a><br />\n<br />\n記住入去睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809be7f75d3a06bb500e8d3c608433348cb8f8fa","tid":521374,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e097906c57ad8844e69b0c89acc24f5e585c4c","tid":521374,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"日人識分香港人同支那人？"},{"pid":"49be5f7ada43908e593f84acc5e0fc4e8d35cae2","tid":521374,"uid":57604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"又話反日無忘南京大屠殺<br />\n轉頭走去支援小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199a4361977b4ff3372a4c1826dc277655de6039","tid":521374,"uid":73310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"71e097906c57ad8844e69b0c89acc24f5e585c4c","tid":521374,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"日人識分香港人同支那人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"識分有禮貌同冇禮貌嘅人<br />\n黎自邊到who cares?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5155af1d00384cab9fd29f57b0c5ecca620171","tid":521374,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話反日無忘南京大屠殺<br />\n轉頭走去支援小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買攻"},{"pid":"a570017bd24b37b27653d98745f30eaa2157fef6","tid":521374,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee41a099738aab33d2f26d03520428213a70a52a","tid":521374,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9d371c5d94675d7bc253727aabf9a7a88a4bf44","tid":521374,"uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人去<del><span style=\"color: red;\">小</span></del><span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>啲日本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小少不分點做中國人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cef3d548c10086695fd0127ba52c217dbd9203a","tid":521374,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a570017bd24b37b27653d98